data.description: Amazing Arrowhead Ranch home just waiting for you!  5 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, over 2500 square feet with a 3 car garage and your own pool all on a quiet cul-de-sac lot!  Vaulted ceilings, recessed lights, plantation shutters, one bedroom and full bath downstairs!  Primary suite upstairs with en suite bath - double sinks, separate tub & shower - and two closets including a walk in!  Kitchen boasts stainless steel appliances, pantry, breakfast bar and stone countertops!  12,000 plus lot, covered patio, garage storage cabinets and much, much more to see!  Sought after Arrowhead Ranch location with EZ freeway access and tons of local dining, shopping, golf and more!
